    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3, a hallmark of the E46 chassis. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the power band. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The vehicle has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and cooling system refreshes, ensuring the structural and thermal integrity required for spirited driving. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain dialed-in for a precise, analog feedback loop. A compelling choice for the purist seeking a turn-key performance icon.",
